1. Can you provide evidence to support the claim that the Indian cricket team was runners-up at the 2003 Cricket World Cup?
2. Is there credible information to back up the statement that the Indian cricket team reached the semifinals in the Cricket World Cups of 1987, 1996, and 2015?
3. Where can verifiable records be found to confirm the Indian cricket team's performance in the mentioned ICC Cricket World Cups?
